snippet.title: Bad Rats: The Rat's Revenge - Trailer
snippet.description:
Computer game Bad Rats: The Rats' Revenge, by Invent4 Entertainment.
Physics puzzle game, where Rats have Cats prisoner, and are ready for revenge.
The game presents comic cartoon violence, and cartoon blood. 
Laughters are surely included when playing, with all humor that the game presents. 
It's all about physics, logic and creativity to have the maps solved. 
Demo available, get it a try and have fun! 
www.invent4.com
